reviewText: This is one of the better B suspense movies I've seen.  Plus I'm a Marc Singer fan, and if you are too, you'll probably like this.  Lots of sex, but that's to be expected from a film of this caliber.  I don't think it detracts from the movie's suspense.  Did I miss something?  What role did Tippy Hedren play?  I didn't notice her, but then, it's been a while.
